WEBVTT

00:00:00.872 --> 00:00:04.208
What happens when a Syrian refugee,

00:00:04.250 --> 00:00:06.210
an Israeli aid worker

00:00:06.252 --> 00:00:09.380
and an American Jew walk into a room?

00:00:09.380 --> 00:00:10.757
(Laughter)

00:00:10.798 --> 00:00:14.719
No, this is not the start
of a really bad joke, I promise.

00:00:15.136 --> 00:00:17.513
This actually happened to me.

00:00:17.555 --> 00:00:20.933
Starting in 2015,

00:00:20.975 --> 00:00:24.479
I found myself holding
a series of secret meetings

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:26.773
in various European capitals

00:00:26.814 --> 00:00:31.319
with a small group of Syrian
and Israeli civilians.